		<DisplayName>Scout Report (The Central Wastes)</DisplayName>
		<Description>A scout comes in your throne room, nervously reporting his findings.
		
		Barbarians in The Central Wastes, thought to be a few scattered tribes, actually number in the tens of thousands if not more.
		
		There's been reports of an individual, likely a Channeler, trying to unite the tribes under one banner.
		
		Your scout thinks it might take up to 15 years to do so, but if he or she was to succeed, it would be the biggest threat you have ever faced.</Description>
