	<QuestDef InternalName="Event_X_GenghisKhan1_330">
		<DisplayName>Scout Report (The Central Wastes)</DisplayName>
		<Description>An injured, haggard, high level scout comes in your throne room. You recognize the man that had first reported on Barbarians 10 years ago. Your men move to help him, but he refuses any help and immediately starts his report.
		
		The Barbarians in The Central Wastes are nearly united under one banner. As a result, an increasing number of skirmishes are taking place on the borders of The Central Wastes, against non-aligned nations.
		
		They are an army unlike any other and if they can not convert you, they will kill you.
		
		Your scout hesitate, in obvious pain, but also, as if pondering whether it is necessary to utter his next words.
		
		They will be here in 5 years at most, he says, as life leaves his broken body.</Description>
